<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>주문/정산</title>
<style type="text/css">
	input[type=checkbox]{
	float: right; 
	width: 20px; 
	height: 20px;
	}
	#sell_span{
		font-size: 18px; 
